### Example 02 — replicate from REST into local DB

### FXService (bundled provider) — direct ping
GET http://localhost:4456/api/rates?limit=3

### Inspect the envelope FXService returns (dataPath target)
GET http://localhost:4456/api/rates?limit=2&offset=0

### Example consumer — target table (possibly empty)
GET http://localhost:4102/odata/v4/example/ExchangeRates?$top=2

### Pipeline tracker row
GET http://localhost:4102/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'ExchangeRates'
